# Action Types Quick Reference for AI

> **Full documentation**: See [docs/interactive-types.md](../docs/interactive-types.md) and [docs/json-block-properties.md](../docs/json-block-properties.md)

## Action Selection Decision Tree

```
User wants to click something:
  └─ Button with stable text → action: "button", reftarget: "Button Text"
  └─ Element with selector → action: "highlight", reftarget: "css-selector"
  └─ Multiple related clicks → type: "multistep" with steps array

User wants to fill form:
  └─ Single field → action: "formfill", reftarget: "selector", targetvalue: "value"
  └─ Validate input → add validateInput: true, formHint: "hint"

User wants to navigate:
  └─ Change pages → action: "navigate", reftarget: "/path"
  └─ With verification → add verify: "on-page:/path"

User wants to reveal hidden UI:
  └─ Hover then click → type: "multistep" with hover + button steps
  └─ User performs manually → type: "guided" with hover + button steps

User wants to teach workflow:
  └─ Linear steps → type: "section" with blocks array
  └─ Just explanation → action: "highlight" with doIt: false
```

## Quick Block Reference

| Block Type    | Purpose                              | Key Properties                    |
|---------------|--------------------------------------|-----------------------------------|
| `interactive` | Single action                        | action, reftarget, content        |
| `section`     | Grouped steps with "Do Section"      | id, title, blocks                 |
| `multistep`   | Automated multi-action               | content, steps                    |
| `guided`      | User-performed with detection        | content, steps, stepTimeout       |
| `conditional` | Show content based on conditions     | conditions, whenTrue, whenFalse   |
| `quiz`        | Knowledge check                      | question, choices                 |
| `input`       | Collect user response                | prompt, inputType, variableName   |
| `markdown`    | Formatted text                       | content                           |
| `image`       | Embedded image                       | src, alt                          |
| `video`       | Embedded video                       | src, provider                     |

## Essential Requirements Pattern

```json
{
  "requirements": ["exists-reftarget"]
}
```

Add based on context:
- Navigation elements: `"navmenu-open"`
- Page-specific: `"on-page:/path"`
- Admin actions: `"is-admin"`
- Data source: `"has-datasource:type"`

## Common Patterns

### Interactive Step
```json
{
  "type": "interactive",
  "action": "highlight",
  "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/dashboards']",
  "requirements": ["navmenu-open", "exists-reftarget"],
  "content": "Click Dashboards"
}
```

### Section with Steps
```json
{
  "type": "section",
  "id": "section-id",
  "title": "Section Title",
  "objectives": ["has-datasource:prometheus"],
  "blocks": [
    { "type": "interactive", "action": "button", "reftarget": "New", "content": "Create" }
  ]
}
```

### Multistep (Automated)
```json
{
  "type": "multistep",
  "content": "Navigate and select",
  "steps": [
    { "action": "button", "reftarget": "Add visualization" },
    { "action": "button", "reftarget": "prometheus" }
  ]
}
```

### Show-Only (Educational)
```json
{
  "type": "interactive",
  "action": "highlight",
  "reftarget": "div[data-testid='panel']",
  "doIt": false,
  "tooltip": "This panel shows metrics.",
  "content": "Notice the metrics panel"
}
```
